main event: In August 1965, a sighting of a flying object was reported in Charles City, Iowa, believed to be an illusion rather than an actual object.
interesting points: The object appeared to have the colors red, green, blue, and white,The sighting was observed at 2020 and looked like a planet, and was divided into two parts,One part moved to the center while the other vanished,The total length of the observation was approximately 45 minutes,The object was attributed to atmospheric conditions and compared to a star or planet.
sighted object: a flying object resembling a planet
witness description: The report did not specify details about the witness.
